					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I don't understand how the time machine can be hurtling through millions of years while still recording a continuous scene of the post-humans getting a cup of whatever.</p> <p>The blackboxed special food seems like a lazy redaction. If you know what it is then say so, or at least hint at it.</p> <p>Overall it seems like a skip I would like, what with the time shenanigans, but there are too many issues for me to enjoy it. Downvote for now.</p> 
